       Deck clients may be interactive or produce document formats such as PDF, HTML or SVG.</text>
     <text xp="20" yp="40" sp="2" wp="50" font="serif" type="block">
       Deck elements are: text, list, image, line, rect, ellipse, arc, curve. 
       Element positions and sizes are only specified in percentages,
       resulting in scalable slides that adapt to any size or orientation.
     </text>
